        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Add an spl_autoload()-compatible autoload() method to the Zend class to make a drop-in callback for autoloading possible. Usage should be:\n{code}\nspl_autoload_register(array('Zend', 'autoload'));\n{code}\nThis can be accomplished by wrapping calls to Zend::loadClass() in a try\/catch block, and returning false if an exception has bee caught."
